short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A dark mode theme for Classtab.org

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This chrome extension enables dark mode themes on the Classtab website (http://www.classtab.org)

There are 4 Available Color Themes:

- Dark Base
- Darcula
- Crimson
- Midnight
